long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: JAWS Inspect is a web developer tool that reports how JAWS screen reader “sees” and “reads” a web page.  With this add-on, you can use the highlight feature to select an element in a report so that you can quickly find it on the web page you are testing. You can also use it to select and highlight an element directly on the web page. Once highlighted, you can run a report on the element or view its HTML properties.  This add-in is meant to be used in conjunction with JAWS Inspect.
